    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A variable color, generally a moderately light warm brownish yellowish color, originally referring to the color of camel hair as used in textiles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
